{"id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0001", "text": "ABN AMRO Editorial.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0001", "source_slug": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan", "source_title": "Cyber ​​Agents attack day and night", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan.html", "source_date": "2025-10-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 1, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0002", "text": "Imagine a digital opponent that is tireless, constantly getting smarter and working completely independently. Self-thinking Cyber ​​Agents threaten the company. Cyber ​​Agents are digital attackers who are active day and night. These self-thinking systems work independently and are becoming increasingly smarter. Experts warn that this technology poses a major challenge for entrepreneurs worldwide.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0002", "source_slug": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan", "source_title": "Cyber ​​Agents attack day and night", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan.html", "source_date": "2025-10-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0003", "text": "Without human guidance.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0003", "source_slug": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan", "source_title": "Cyber ​​Agents attack day and night", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan.html", "source_date": "2025-10-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0004", "text": "Cyber Agents are autonomous programs that scan networks for weaknesses. They attack without human guidance. Unlike classic malware, they work as digital hunters. They immediately adjust their approach if systems defend themselves better. Why Cyber Agents are Dangerous. The biggest risk is their speed and scale.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0004", "source_slug": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan", "source_title": "Cyber ​​Agents attack day and night", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan.html", "source_date": "2025-10-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0005", "text": "A human hacker can only attack one system at a time. Cyber ​​Agents can attack thousands of systems simultaneously, day and night.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0005", "source_slug": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan", "source_title": "Cyber ​​Agents attack day and night", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan.html", "source_date": "2025-10-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0006", "text": "They are difficult to stop and almost impossible to trace back to a perpetrator.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0006", "source_slug": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan", "source_title": "Cyber ​​Agents attack day and night", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan.html", "source_date": "2025-10-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0007", "text": "Future music, but not far away. This technology is still in development, but reality is getting closer. Experts expect that entrepreneurs will soon have to deal with this threat. It is important to take steps now. Think of better collaboration, sharing information and strengthening digital infrastructure. Prepare the company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0007", "source_slug": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan", "source_title": "Cyber ​​Agents attack day and night", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan.html", "source_date": "2025-10-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0008", "text": "Cyber Agents herald a new era in cyber threats. Machines fight machines. This emphasizes the need for strong digital defense. Protect your company by investing in cybersecurity in a timely manner. Don't wait until it's too late.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0008", "source_slug": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan", "source_title": "Cyber ​​Agents attack day and night", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan.html", "source_date": "2025-10-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0009", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://www.samendigitaalveilig.nl/).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0009", "source_slug": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan", "source_title": "Cyber ​​Agents attack day and night", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan.html", "source_date": "2025-10-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0010", "text": "Take cyber measures yourself or report fraud? About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company. Do you have an SME company and do you want to reduce your cyber risks? Then take a look at [Cyber ​​Fundament](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-voor-het-mkb/), especially for SME entrepreneurs. Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) especially for large businesses and reduce your cyber risks. Do you also want to [do business safely](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link)? View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars.\n[Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately. Tags. [Knowledge article](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/actueel.html). [Cyber attack](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberattack/index.html).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan__c6-semantic__0010", "source_slug": "cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan", "source_title": "Cyber ​​Agents attack day and night", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/cyber-agents-vallen-dag-en-nacht-aan.html", "source_date": "2025-10-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_wi